data.description: Step into the epitome of exquisite living with this captivating trilevel home that seamlessly combines custom craftsmanship, abundant natural light, and true character. Boasting four generously sized bedrooms and two meticulously designed bathrooms, this residence exudes charm at every turn. Revel in the allure of newer paint and laminate flooring that graces the interior, creating a modern and inviting atmosphere. The kitchen, a focal point of sophistication, features an open layout adorned with custom cabinets, granite countertops, and top-of-the-line appliances. Delight in the exclusive addition of a private bar, an ideal haven for entertaining guests. Nestled in an enviable location with access to District 11 schools, this home sits on a sprawling lot surrounded by meticulously fenced front and back yards, offering a perfect blend of privacy and outdoor space. Parking is a breeze with the inclusion of RV parking and a two-car garage. From upgraded flooring to the pride of ownership evident throughout, this turnkey gem is ready to embrace its new owners with unmatched elegance and style. Don't miss the opportunity to make this residence your own - a testament to quality living and refined taste.
